Cult of Silence - Yoshi's Island - Flowe.info: The melody is swapped with the song "Привет с большого бодуна" (Privet s bol'shogo boduna, "Hello from the big hangover") by the band Дюна (Dyuna).

hashtagmashup.info: "#mashup" is a Russian community of enthusiasts who make music mash-ups with all kinds of stuff. Their primary spot is their group on VK.

Александр Спирс - Шесть токсичных кадров.info: A mash-up of "Toxic" by Britney Spears and the intro song from the Russian comedy sketch TV show "6 кадров" (Shest' kadrov,"6 Frames").

ВИКТОР ЦОЙ и Kavinsky - Группа Крови (za.info: A mash-up of "Protovision" by Kavinsky and the song "Группа крови" (Gruppa krovi, "Blood group") by the band "Кино" (Kino).

Дибензилкетон х дачник - What a wonderfu.info: A cover of "What A Wonderful World" by Louis Armstrong with lyrics from #mashup's in-joke meme song "На барабане крутится дерьмо" (Na barabane krutitsya der'mo, "Shit is spinning on the wheel") by The Свитер (The Sviter).

иЛуаЗ_ x baZZZarov - Если в убежище живё.info: A mash-up of "Shelter" by Porter Robinson & Madeon and the song "Если в сердце живёт любовь" (Yesli v serdtse zhivyot lyubov', "If love lives in the heart") by Юлия Савичева (Yuliya Savicheva), which was the theme song for a TV series I don't remember.

Ильяс Лем - Гонщик нелегальный.info: A mash-up of "Running In the 90's" by Max Coveri and #mashup's in-joke meme song "Гонщик нелегальный" (Gonshchik nelegal'nyy, "Illegal racer") by MC Dimanche.

неплохая пица - фрустрация шуфутинского.info: A mash-up of "Snowfall" from "VA-11 Hall-A" and the song "Третье Сентября" (Tret'ye Sentyabrya, The third of September) by Михаил Шуфутинский (Mikhail Shufutinsky).

осторожно постмодерн - пастушенко маст д.info: A mash-up of "Invaders Must Die" by The Prodigy and the song "Reach Up (Papa's Got A Brand New Pigbag)" by Perfecto Allstarz, which was the intro song for the Russian comedy TV show "Осторожно, модерн!" (Ostorozhno, modern!, "Beware, modernism!").

any34 - Такси увезло в Японию.info: A mash-up of "Silky Heart" by Yui Horie and the song "Такси, такси" (Taxi, taxi) by Игорь Николаев (Igor' Nikolayev) and Наташа Королёва (Natasha Korolyova).
